    public interface SnomedMRCMAttributeRangeRefSetMember
extends SnomedRefSetMember
    A representation of the model object 'Snomed MRCM Attribute Range Ref Set Member'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Range Constraint
    • Attribute Rule
    • Rule Strength Id
    • Content Type Id
